int next = (i == flowerbed.length - 1) ? 0 : flowerbed[i + 1];


Kid explanation:

Left neighbor

If this is the first pot, pretend left is empty

Right neighbor

If this is the last pot, pretend right is empty

So edges are handled safely ðŸ›¡ï¸

5ï¸âƒ£ Can we plant here?
if(prev == 0 && next == 0)


This means:

Left pot is empty âœ…

Right pot is empty âœ…

ðŸŽ‰ SAFE SPOT FOUND!

6ï¸âƒ£ Plant the flower ðŸŒ¸
